'''Skylane T-534D''' was a [[Skyways Flyer]] skylane in the [[Fobosi District/Legends|Fobosi District]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], an accident was caused by a malfunctioning automated [[pubtrans flitter]] that went the wrong direction. Five speeder vehicles avoiding the flitter collided into an unmanned water silo, which was breached and flooded the apartments below. [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Lott Dod/Legends|Lott Dod]] was one of the six accident victims and was rushed to a medical unit.

